 KB · \nTodays price action & anticipation of his speech (and SBR announcement) did play out like BTC nashville speech with a \"full retrace\"\n\nSince no crypto was mentioned, no SBR or purchasing BTC, I ended up taking no long positions today, however, a pro-crypto EO might still come today or during coming days with the form of a \"headline\"/ text , so I am staying on my toes\n\nI did however take a short position on BTC, which was too fast that I couldnt possibly share it in real time on Telegram\n\nThis tweet from Bloomberg guy was my trigger for entry and second screenshot is my exit at 101.000 flat\n4.3K\n\n02:12","timestamp":"4.3K\n\n02:12","images":["blob:https://web.telegram.org/deb0c8f5-9321-4665-a6f1-71f14fff4ecb","blob:https://web.telegram.org/6809be6d-7e3b-4ac4-9340-2b10db66ad8f","blob:https://web.telegram.org/c68faf12-9441-47b3-b593-eaa66667cf6f"],"links":[],"videos":[]},{"text":"RunnerXBT\n\nTomorrow, January 21st is Microstrategy shareholder meeting.\n\nMicroStrategy plans to increase authorized shares to support its Bitcoin purchasing strategy.\n\nKey focus of the vote will be to approve an increase in authorized Class A common stock from 330 million shares to 10.3 billion shares. Shareholders will also consider raising the number of authorized preferred shares from 5 million to 1 billion.\n\nI think Saylor can bring some headlines again tomorrow. Not just Trump and pro-crypto Executive Orders\n\nsources\nCrypto Briefing\nMicroStrategy shareholders to decide on major stock increase to advance Bitcoin strategy tomorrow\nMicroStrategy shareholders to decide on expanding stock issuance for Bitcoin strategy, supporting a $42 billion capital plan.\n5.1K\n\n02:24","timestamp":"5.1K\n\n02:24","images":["blob:https://web.telegram.org/e6a166bd-b555-49b3-9463-e73606d746db"],"links":["https://cryptobriefing.com/microstrategy-bitcoin-strategy-shareholders-vote/","https://cryptobriefing.com/microstrategy-bitcoin-strategy-shareholders-vote/","https://cryptobriefing.com/microstrategy-bitcoin-strategy-shareholders-vote/"],"videos":[]},{"text":"RunnerXBT\n\ntg_image_2385151038.png\n309 KB · \nI am giving Trump's speech one last time\n\nHe will be shortly speaking on his little podium and after/during the event signing some EOs (Executive Orders), that is a table with bunch of books (filled with EOs)\n\nstream on his Twitter: https://x.com/realDonaldTrump/status/1881419736648499257\n4.9K\n\n07:01","timestamp":"4.9K\n\n07:01","images":["blob:https://web.telegram.org/9d7a4056-6548-4e24-b31b-27a0f6f0a104"],"links":["https://x.com/realDonaldTrump/status/1881419736648499257"],"videos":[]},{"text":"RunnerXBT\n\nExtremely underwhelming, all day\n\nPeople got excited on Twitter leak and since BTC has just been down only. Trump delivered (so far) zero \"Day 1\" promises for Crypto.\n4.8K\n\n08:03","timestamp":"4.8K\n\n08:03","images":[],"links":[],"videos":[]}],"2025-01-22":[{"text":"January 22, 2025","timestamp":"","images":[],"links":[],"videos":[]}],"2025-01-23":[{"text":"RunnerXBT\n\nRunnerXBT\nTomorrow, January 21st is Microstrategy shareholder meeting. MicroStrategy plans to increase author...\nBWENEWS: MicroStrategy shareholders approve increasing shares from 330M to 10.3B (55.8% approval), clearing a path for more #Bitcoin acquisitions. https://x.com/Cointelegraph/status/1881729687275397328\nX (formerly Twitter)\nCointelegraph (@Cointelegraph) on X\n️ JUST IN: MicroStrategy shareholders approve increasing shares from 330M to 10.3B (55.8% approval), clearing a path for more #Bitcoin acquisitions.\n5.1K\n\n00:08","timestamp":"5.1K\n\n00:08","images":["blob:https://web.telegram.org/b9cc0cf5-09c1-49a9-8252-58e41f88281a","https://web.telegram.org/k/assets/img/emoji/26a1.png","blob:https://web.telegram.org/039e347b-22fe-40aa-9cbe-0be093cd4dbc"],"links":["tg://search_hashtag?hashtag=Bitcoin","https://x.com/Cointelegraph/status/1881729687275397328","https://x.com/Cointelegraph/status/1881729687275397328","https://x.com/Cointelegraph/status/1881729687275397328","tg://search_hashtag?hashtag=Bitcoin"],"videos":[]}],"2025-01-24":[{"text":"January 24, 2025","timestamp":"","images":[],"links":[],"videos":[]},{"text":"RunnerXBT\n\ntg_image_4233457864.png\n204 KB · \ntg_image_2258420030.tiff\n1.4 MB · \nVery eventful day today filled with 3 intra-day trading opportunities. \nIn this post I will cover all 3 of them, how I traded first 2 and how I plan to trade the third one coming up.\n\nDisclaimer: If you dont really day-trade, this might not be a post for you, however perhaps you can pick-up something when it comes to decision making on LTFs.\n\nInitial context: Its President Trumps 4th day in the office and first 10-30 days are historically most impactful as most Executive Orders and decisions are made\n\nTrade 1:\nSenator Lummis posts on X \"Big Things are coming, Stay tuned for 10 AM\" (Link)\n\nMy reasoning: Lummis is a long-term BTC/Crypto bull, has been public for a long time, she was proponent of SBR and BTC-Bill, however, she is \"just a senator\" and no way she has power to announce anything that would REALLY move the market. I expect her announcement to be \"nothingburger\" and decided to short in advance as i was 95% confident this would be a sell the news.\n\nBTC moved 4% from her tweet, which is frankly insane if you ask me.\n\nMarket being so extremely excited for any pro-crypto headline and desperate for SBR headline moved up with leverage.\n\n10 AM came and it was \"Honored to chair the Senate Banking Subcommittee on Digital Assets.\"\n\nWhich is obviously great news but did not meet expectations of the market and it sold off.\n\nFirst Image is chart \nSecond Image is my execution\n\nSecond and third trade coming shortly.\n4.6K\n\n01:25","timestamp":"4.6K\n\n01:25","images":["blob:https://web.telegram.org/1014167a-8555-479b-80f9-8b599ff0f4fc","blob:https://web.telegram.org/1137fe1a-c861-4682-ab58-615d146ca9e6"],"links":["https://x.com/SenLummis/status/1882432096783778270"],"videos":[]},{"text":"Trade 2:\nHeadline on Twitter (Link) & Donald Trump speaking online at WEF in Davos in which he mentions \"USA to become capital of AI and crypto\"\n\nMy reasoning: Crypto community got excited about the El Salvador headline, because it is a country that was first to adopt BTC and its Volcano Bonds (TLDR: Pro crypto country), again a \"naive\" crypto community ran with the headline as if President Trump was going to talk to Mr. Bukele about Bitcoin.\n\nA cherry on the top was him mentioning \"Capital of crypto\".\n\nI started shorting again, as I expect him ending his WEF speech as sell the news\n\nWhy I wasnt afraid of the El Salvador headline, I will discuss in Trade 3) below in a second\n\nFirst Image is chart\nSecond Image is my execution\n\nThird trade goes hand in hand with 3rd trade\n5.1K\n\n01:31","timestamp":"5.1K\n\n01:31","images":["blob:https://web.telegram.org/d8bc8d91-5ec5-42be-ba91-d8e9fda38ec3","blob:https://web.telegram.org/83de4451-4caf-4332-a0d1-77f11fc34b89"],"links":["https://x.com/DeItaone/status/1882449190674203123"],"videos":[]}],"2025-01-25":[{"text":"Trade 3: (Yet to play out - multiple scenarios)\nHeadline on Twitter (Link ) Trump to hold a call with President of El Salvador at 3:30 PM ET, Trump to sign EO 1 hour sooner\n\nMy reasoning: This will be a bit more nuanced and longer version than previous 2 as its in the future and isnt easier hindsight analysis.\nCrypto community is, as per usual, expecting Trump and El Salvador Bukele to discuss Bitcoin, Bitcoin strategy and Bitcoin reserves/bonds (the \"best possible scenario\" if you will)\n\nI do personally think, that Trump and his admin do like crypto and will be pro-crypto (as we have seen him launch 2 SOL shitcoins $TRUMP and $MELANIA), however on 4th day of presidency, when he has not even spoken to Putin about ending war in Ukraine, does he REALLY prioritize crypto talk? we are yet to see\n\nWhat I think the call and executive order today will be around is Migration/Deportation and around such topics (borders...), therefore AGAIN, a disappointment for crypto community\nHow am I going to approach it step by step with time stamps. I really do believe I am making a mistake by sharing step by step but what I wouldnt do for my friends right :wink:\n\nat 2:30 PM ET (8:30 CET or 20:30 for my Euro friends) an Executive Order will be uploaded / hit the news aggregators and scrapers\nLink to White House website, personally I think you are going to be a bit faster just following on Twitter (DB, Tree of Alpha, Zoomer...)\n\nat 2:30 PM ET we will instantly see: \"is it Crypto, or not?\"\n\nif yes -> giga turbo mega long my longs (my personal probability 5%)\nif no -> expecting same disappointing outcome, a bit off BTC sell-off, as with Two trades mentioned above (my personal probability 95%)\n\nif yes -> market buy BTC with size (if BTC strategic reserve is mentioned)\nif no -> market sell BTC with size (as BTC is going to go down few % intraday again)\n\nRegardless of Yes/No, I dont plan to overstay my welcome, I expect to hold the trade for few minutes maximum, if we really would get BTC SBR and USA to buy Billions of BTC, maybe I want to hold that long a bit longer\n\nGiven the context mentioned thru these posts/essay (whatever you want to call it), I believe its unlikely for Trump to discuss Bitcoin on 4th day of his presidency\nHOWEVER, if he does, that is TRULY our best long-signal ever.\n\nClosing words: I think we will get pro-crypto headlines and executive orders eventually, I just dont see them as their priority, nor should it be. For crypto we have a pro-crypto friendly teams like SEC and CFTC and afformentioned Sen Lummis :-) \n\nWill update once EO hits the website. Good luck\nedited\n5.9K\n\n01:45","timestamp":"edited\n5.9K\n\n01:45","images":["blob:https://web.telegram.org/ef8ad042-5612-4b01-aa81-3ddba7a74445"],"links":["https://x.com/DeItaone/status/1882449190674203123","https://www.whitehouse.gov/presidential-actions/"],"videos":[]},{"text":"RunnerXBT\n\napologies was mistake in the time zones (feel free to Google/to convert to your timezones)\n\nEO comes 2:30 PM ET which is 20:30 Prague time (long and tiring day sorry)\n\n90 minutes to go basically!\n6.4K\n\n01:56","timestamp":"6.4K\n\n01:56","images":[],"links":[],"videos":[]},{"text":"RunnerXBT\n\nholy shit \n\nEO related to crypto (no details yet?)\n6.1K\n\n04:14","timestamp":"6.1K\n\n04:14","images":[],"links":[],"videos":[]}],"2025-01-26":[{"text":"(not longin myself)\n6.3K\n\n04:14","timestamp":"6.3K\n\n04:14","images":[],"links":[],"videos":[]},{"text":"well SBR announced so gg\n6.8K\n\n04:26","timestamp":"6.8K\n\n04:26","images":["blob:https://web.telegram.org/dbac37af-9053-4cc9-bb75-83d5811c83e5"],"links":[],"videos":[]}],"2025-01-27":[{"text":"January 27, 2025","timestamp":"","images":[],"links":[],"videos":[]},{"text":"a lot of derisking since CME open, imo due to multiple factors\n\n-1st degree of importance: DeepSeek (read: website)\n-2nd degree of importance: busy macro events week from Wednesday to Friday + Tech stocks earnings\n-3rd degree of importance: USA imposing tarriffs on countries\n\nTLDR: AI stuff is pulling down equities, which are pulling down BTC, altcoins? yes\nChinese AI was trained for peanuts and US (global) market is realizing some of these AI valuations are ?overblown?\nedited\n9.2K\n\n16:30","timestamp":"edited\n9.2K\n\n16:30","images":["blob:https://web.telegram.org/80fdbd3a-faca-4625-b2f3-3c0ff1ce35e1"],"links":["https://finance.yahoo.com/news/nasdaq-futures-slump-china-deepseek-022904517.html"],"videos":[]},{"text":"RunnerXBT\n\n*BTC DOWN 7%\n*GOLD DOWN 1%\n\n*PRE-MARKET MOVES:\nMETA DOWN 4.5%\nTESLA DOWN 4%\nNVIDIA DOWN 8%\nGOOGLE DOWN 3.2%\nAMAZON DOWN 3.2%\nMICROSOFT DOWN 3.5%\nBROADCOM DOWN 8%\n\nLikely Reasons:\n*China's AI Fear, China developing AI despite huge sanctions by US on GPUs \n*China's deepseek has surpassed ChatGPT in App store rankings, Meta in panic mode, fear deepseek is better than upcoming Llama 4..\n*BOJ raised interest rates to 17 years high\n*First FOMC meeting under Trump & Major Tech Earnings coming this week..\n6.3K\n\n17:01","timestamp":"6.3K\n\n17:01","images":[],"links":[],"videos":[]},{"text":"RunnerXBT\n\nU.S. STOCK INDEX FUTURES EXTEND LOSSES; S&P 500 E-MINI FUTURES DOWN 2.3%, NASDAQ FUTURES SLIDE 4%, DOW FUTURES FALL 1%\n5.6K\n\n18:42","timestamp":"5.6K\n\n18:42","images":[],"links":[],"videos":[]},{"text":"RunnerXBT\n\n$NVDA - AI-LINKED STOCKS EXTEND PREMARKET LOSSES\n\nNVIDIA DOWN 11.3%, BROADCOM DOWN 14.1%\n\n—————-\n\nExpecting markets to stabilize between Thursday/Friday this week\n\nVIX +40%\n5.9K\n\n19:45","timestamp":"5.9K\n\n19:45","images":[],"links":[],"videos":[]}],"2025-01-28":[{"text":"January 28, 2025","timestamp":"","images":[],"links":[],"videos":[]}],"2025-01-07":[{"text":"RunnerXBT\n\n$NVDA -17% TODAY\n\nhttps://finance.yahoo.com/news/live/stock-market-today-nasdaq-sinks-sp-500-tumbles-as-ai-fears-rock-tech-stocks-143116264.html\nYahoo Finance\nStock market today: Nasdaq clobbered, Nvidia sinks 17% while Dow stages comeback...\nA Chinese startup's promise of cheaper AI has rattled faith in the growth prospects for tech stocks.\n6.8K\n\n00:33","timestamp":"6.8K\n\n00:33","images":["blob:https://web.telegram.org/97dba27a-816d-449a-9270-82c0975468d8"],"links":["https://finance.yahoo.com/news/live/stock-market-today-nasdaq-sinks-sp-500-tumbles-as-ai-fears-rock-tech-stocks-143116264.html","https://finance.yahoo.com/news/live/stock-market-today-nasdaq-sinks-sp-500-tumbles-as-ai-fears-rock-tech-stocks-143116264.html","https://finance.yahoo.com/news/live/stock-market-today-nasdaq-sinks-sp-500-tumbles-as-ai-fears-rock-tech-stocks-143116264.html"],"videos":[]}],"2024-12-16":[{"text":"December 16, 2024","timestamp":"","images":[],"links":[],"videos":[]}],"2024-12-17":[{"text":"RunnerXBT\n\n= they will buy 600m of BTC\n\n(they did 500m last week)\n4.6K\n\n22:01","timestamp":"4.6K\n\n22:01","images":[],"links":[],"videos":[]},{"text":"Inauguration day\n\nBTC SBR apparently \"leaked\" on Twitter, hence a move to 110k overnight, asked bunch of my smart friends, everybody is pointing out to a leak\n\ncould be really ugly if there is no BTC SBR Executive Order within today\n\n(Personally I dont trust rumours or leaks)\nedited\n9.1K\n\n16:45","timestamp":"edited\n9.1K\n\n16:45","images":["blob:https://web.telegram.org/77ebfc24-8be8-4403-93a7-f3b6df3d3d20"],"links":[],"videos":[]}],"2024-12-18":[{"text":"December 18, 2024","timestamp":"","images":[],"links":[],"videos":[]},{"text":"From CryptoCred\n4.6K\n\n18:26","timestamp":"4.6K\n\n18:26","images":["blob:https://web.telegram.org/e7acb6ed-7e40-4a5d-91c7-f64b4491b5a9"],"links":[],"videos":[]}],"2024-12-19":[{"text":"December 19, 2024","timestamp":"","images":[],"links":[],"videos":[]}],"2024-12-20":[{"text":"RunnerXBT\n\nFOMC yesterday delivered big.\nJerome Powell speech spooked the market and resulted in 4% correction in SP500. VIX (Volatility index) went up almost 100% in the same timeframe.\n\nCrypto isnt immune and dumped with it, while BTC poked below 100k for a brief moment, I closed our short position on BTC.\n\nI do believe this was a (local) bottom for at least few days (i know not very generous of me)\n\nMy reasoning is simple\n- VIX going parabolic always results in a nuke in markets which is almost always a great buy. Last time it happened was big liquidation cascade on August 5th (Surprise Bank of Japan Hike/Cut)\n- TradFi is already recovering pre-market\n\nI highly encourage you to do this homework, look at all peaks on VIX (daily/weekly chart) and overlay it with BTC price action\n\nOur positioning\n- 100% BTC spot long (looking to start hedging again as I believe week of December 23rd should be slow due to holidays/EoY\n- Long SOL (around 20% of desired position size so far)\n\nalmost 800 mil usd liquidations in last 24hrs, hopefully nobody here got hit\n5.4K\n\n22:27","timestamp":"5.4K\n\n22:27","images":[],"links":[],"videos":[]}],"2024-12-22":[{"text":"image_2024-12-19_15-27-24.png\n61 KB · \nimage_2024-12-19_15-27-24.png\n53 KB · \n5.6K\n\n22:27","timestamp":"5.6K\n\n22:27","images":["blob:https://web.telegram.org/8a2fbde5-234c-4d72-b70d-f0ce80f288a4","blob:https://web.telegram.org/bd27648d-73ae-43d7-b881-291b0e23689f"],"links":[],"videos":[]}],"2024-12-23":[{"text":"This is my favorite \"long\" signal, on bad macro fears/headlines\n6.3K\n\n22:30","timestamp":"6.3K\n\n22:30","images":["blob:https://web.telegram.org/847a2657-32c9-4217-86ca-c87f9c1db9e6"],"links":[],"videos":[]}],"2024-12-25":[{"text":"December 25, 2024","timestamp":"","images":[],"links":[],"videos":[]},{"text":"RunnerXBT\n\nno crypto mention nor BTC Strategic reserves at all during his \"Victory celebration speech\" which just ended \n\nat least their team managed to launch a memecoin for his wife (please do not buy it...)\nedited\n4.3K\n\n07:18","timestamp":"edited\n4.3K\n\n07:18","images":[],"links":[],"videos":[]}],"2025-01-06":[{"text":"RunnerXBT\n\nimage_2024-12-24_23-15-09.png\n296 KB · \nTodays move has been Binance spot and Binance Perps led, Coinbase followed afterwards. There was also no Coinbase Premium\n\nWhat I am trying to say is that I dont think it was Saylor or ETFs buying today (due to Holidays/shorter Work Day in TradFi) but Binance Degens \n\nWhich has not happened in a long time. Finally.\n\nWishing everybody a Merry X-mas & Happy New Year\n8.4K\n\n06:15","timestamp":"8.4K\n\n06:15","images":["blob:https://web.telegram.org/6880b63f-303b-4731-8e87-cf5bb128f4ef"],"links":[],"videos":[]}],"2025-01-18":[{"text":"January 18, 2025","timestamp":"","images":[],"links":[],"videos":[]},{"text":"RunnerXBT\n\ntg_image_1146671305.png\n165 KB · \ntg_image_2350210468.png\n217 KB · \nJanuary 17th 2025 Update:\nToday is Friday (last working day) before Donald Trump Inauguration on Monday. Monday is a holiday and markets are closed (we have 3 day weekend)\n\nSince US open (2hrs 15 min ago) there was insane spike in buying on all fronts (see chart) with meaningful Coinbase premium\nI suspect Michael Saylor and ETFs (boomers in general) and also retail market participants (me and you both) are FOMOing extremely hard due to SBR (Strategic Bitcoin Reserve) narrative\n\nand the last day when one could traditionally FOMO, with good liquidity is... well Today\n\nThis extreme sentiment optimism and flip-flopping (as people were calling for end of the world just last week due to Macro conditions) is very normal in times of volatility.\n\nSecond image shows orderflow data, Open Interest (effectively amount of leverage in the system) is going parabolic today and this often leads to both sides of the market getting punished.\n\nI do expect volatility to calm down as US session ends and then I will try to get as much rest as possible for Monday/Tuesday/Wednesday as I will be glued to my PC 24/7.\n\nIt is obvious to me that market is expecting BSR news to drop on Monday or Tuesday the latest. anticipation is very high. Makes me wonder if its another BTC Nashville moment (July 27th 2024)\n\nas we are 100% spot BTC, I have to consider multiple scenarios\n\n1) SBR gets announced day 1 (Monday) or Tuesday the latest -> enjoy pump to a lot fucking higher\n\n2) SBR doesnt get announced instantly, overleveraged market starts panicking, woala a recipe for disaster -> i will hedge some of our BTC spot via BTC futs short\n\nNobody knows when and how SBR announcement looks like, but TLDR its obvious that our entire price action in the coming days and weeks revolves around this ONE event alone\n\nI am personally not sure this is time to be a hero.\n\nGood luck to all of us. Update on Monday/Tuesday.\n3.9K\n\n00:52","timestamp":"3.9K\n\n00:52","images":["blob:https://web.telegram.org/9620e48a-b691-468c-bc05-fd5a3a77a0e3","blob:https://web.telegram.org/7701651d-276e-4af3-81f4-51c9136f00fe"],"links":[],"videos":[]},{"text":"BTC nashville example\n\nit was (felt) exactly the same, community expected insane speech from (now) President Trump, yet it was underwhelming due to the fact that market pumped super hard leading into it.\n\nI am not saying that I expect it necessarily to be classic sell-the-news event\n\nbut if (very eager) community doesnt get exactly what they want, i expect lots of longs covering\n3.9K\n\n00:55","timestamp":"3.9K\n\n00:55","images":["blob:https://web.telegram.org/eec9f568-f3a2-473b-b6f2-afe9f1c2db57"],"links":[],"videos":[]},{"text":"if anybody is in the same boat like me (100% BTC spot long)\n\nI am not looking to open ANY shorts until when US session is about to end (4 hrs from time of writing this) \nto ensure that Michael Saylor doesnt ape another 9-10 figures on my head\nedited\n3.9K\n\n00:56","timestamp":"edited\n3.9K\n\n00:56","images":[],"links":[],"videos":[]}],"2025-01-19":[{"text":"Polymarket isnt the most \"liquid\" venue to bet on the outcome, but definitely a proxy for sentiment\n7.2K\n\n01:04","timestamp":"7.2K\n\n01:04","images":["blob:https://web.telegram.org/f559f31a-06ba-4a51-b550-80c818347c18"],"links":[],"videos":[]},{"text":"RunnerXBT\n\nand lastly on SBR (Strategic Bitcoin Reserve)\nI think there is important caveat and factors to consider\n\n1) Does it happen (Yes/No)\n2) When is it announced? And when does it go into \"action\" (I read something that Bill in USA takes a few months to go into action)\n\nand most importantly 3) which coins?\n3a) is it simply the DOJ seized coins that are NOT sold and turned into SBR (without additional coins being purchased)\n3b) is it USA GOV buying a small amount of BTC (say 500m) is there a budget/cap?\n3c) USA GOV goes full Michal Saylor and buys billions\nedited\n4.1K\n\n01:17","timestamp":"edited\n4.1K\n\n01:17","images":[],"links":[],"videos":[]},{"text":"Bitcoins momentum has slowed down significantly since US session closed. Not expecting much to happen until Monday since everyone will be looking